As for emergency, they can be a help in a xp group for those &quot;oops&quot; moments when the group find itself LOM and the room just spawned. I have an enchanter alt (lv 54) and I have found my self in situations where just a little more mana could have made the difference to get in that last mez. Of course these type of situations are few and far in between.<br>
<br>
So, I would say that emergency mana increases in value with the difficulty of the place you are hunting. <br>
